# Branding Guidelines

- The official name of the application is **SailsPipeline**.
- Always capitalize the **S** and the **P** (PascalCase) when referencing the software in UI components, headers, and automated client/agent emails.
- Ensure the login screen, browser tab title, and dashboard headers reflect **SailsPipeline CRM**.
- Use shared constants: `frontend/src/branding.ts` and `backend/app/branding.py`.
